Package: linux-headers-server-lts-backport-maverick
Architecture: amd64 i386
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-server [amd64], linux-headers-generic-pae-lts-backport-maverick [i386]
Description: Linux kernel headers on Server Equipment.
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel headers available
 for Server Equipment.

Package: linux-image-server-lts-backport-maverick
Architecture: amd64 i386
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-server [amd64], linux-firmware [amd64], linux-image-generic-pae-lts-backport-maverick [i386]
Description: Linux kernel image on Server Equipment.
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel image available
 for Server Equipment.

Package: linux-server-lts-backport-maverick
Architecture: amd64 i386
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-server-lts-backport-maverick (= ${binary:Version}) [amd64], linux-generic-pae-lts-backport-maverick [i386]
Description: Complete Linux kernel on Server Equipment.
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Linux kernel available
 for Server Equipment.

